Package: CFT
Type: Package
Title: Biometric Models for Canadian Forests 
Version: 0.1.5
Author: Mathieu Fortin
Maintainer: Mathieu Fortin <mathieu.fortin.re@gmail.com>
Description: Provide some models applied to forestry that were developed in the Canadian context. 
   At the moment, this package implements (i) an estimator of the beta diversity and (ii) an estimator
   of GHG emissions. The package relies on the J4R package and the Java libraries repicea and mrnf-foresttools which are licensed under the LGPL 3.0 license. See the website for further details. 
URL: https://sourceforge.net/p/mrnfforesttools/wiki/CFT/
Depends: R (>= 3.4.0)
Imports: 
    J4R (>= 1.0.7),
    graphics,
    methods, 
    stats, 
    utils
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.1.0
SystemRequirements: Java 8
Suggests: 
    testthat
